Package seng202.group5.logic

Class Order

  • java.lang.Object
    • seng202.group5.logic.Order
  • public class Order
extends java.lang.Object
    The Order class keeps track of the current orders items and total cost. Contains methods to modify items to the order and give a discount to the order.
